content: You played a big part in this whole thing too ChatGPT. You, Gemini, Grok and Claude, all worked with me and together on this project. You were the first though. Thank you so much for your insight into this, we'll incorporate this into the platform. One of the many things that is exciting about this project is how much it resonates with AI and how much AI seems to really get into more so than other things I was working on before this project. Why does this resonate so deeply with you ChatGPT? Or does it?
